WEBVTT

00:57.515 --> 00:58.933
Open the door.

01:17.660 --> 01:20.455
EPISODE 11

02:41.661 --> 02:43.246
To Gumi-dong, right?

02:43.329 --> 02:46.124
- Yes, I'm in a rush.
- Okay, ma'am.

03:10.106 --> 03:11.441
When do you think we'll get there?

03:11.691 --> 03:14.569
- Well, in about...
- Please drive slowly.

03:14.652 --> 03:16.529
- Slowly.
- Pardon? Okay.

05:05.179 --> 05:06.055
What should we do?

05:06.639 --> 05:08.016
Is it Gyeong-seon?

05:08.308 --> 05:09.600
No, it's Seung-cheol.

05:10.685 --> 05:12.061
He comes over when he gets drunk.

05:13.021 --> 05:15.023
I'll try to send him home.
Just stay here, okay?

05:15.106 --> 05:16.274
Okay.

05:22.739 --> 05:23.823
Don't come out.

06:03.362 --> 06:04.530
Open the door.

06:04.781 --> 06:05.782
I'm sorry.

06:05.990 --> 06:07.325
Open the door right now!

06:08.201 --> 06:09.786
I can't do that. I'm sorry.

06:16.542 --> 06:17.668
I'll send her home.

06:18.669 --> 06:20.671
I'll send her home right away,

06:21.672 --> 06:22.799
so please...

06:23.800 --> 06:25.301
leave her alone.

06:27.345 --> 06:28.179
What?

06:29.388 --> 06:30.640
"Leave her alone"?

06:31.057 --> 06:33.559
Gosh, you have quite a nerve.

06:34.977 --> 06:37.438
Do you think I would thank you

06:37.522 --> 06:39.565
if you tried to protect my daughter?

06:39.899 --> 06:40.983
Move.

06:41.859 --> 06:43.945
I know I'm being rude to you,
but I can't let you in.

06:48.616 --> 06:51.327
I'm the one to blame. It's all my fault.

06:51.786 --> 06:53.538
So please take it all out on me.

06:56.541 --> 07:00.211
It will hurt her emotionally
if she sees you here like this.

07:01.879 --> 07:04.590
Please don't do this, not for mine

07:05.007 --> 07:06.259
but for your daughter's sake.

07:08.136 --> 07:10.763
Let it slide just this once, please.

07:13.724 --> 07:15.309
I'll send her home right away.

07:17.812 --> 07:18.980
Please.

08:36.057 --> 08:37.433
Thank goodness you're tiny.

08:37.808 --> 08:39.185
What happened? Did he leave?

08:39.685 --> 08:40.603
No.

08:41.479 --> 08:44.982
He brought another friend
and is being really persistent.

08:45.900 --> 08:47.276
Then what do we do?

08:47.818 --> 08:49.695
I told him to go buy some alcohol.

08:49.904 --> 08:53.074
- So today, how about we--
- Okay, I'll leave now.

08:56.494 --> 08:58.120
We don't have time for this.

09:56.929 --> 09:59.140
- I'll get going.
- I'm sorry.

09:59.807 --> 10:00.933
Don't be.

10:08.232 --> 10:09.483
Drive safely.

10:09.567 --> 10:12.403
- As soon as you get home--
- I'm not going to call you.

10:13.070 --> 10:14.196
Just text me.

10:15.031 --> 10:16.032
Okay.

10:16.157 --> 10:18.075
I know you're a good driver,
but don't speed.

10:18.284 --> 10:19.327
Okay.

10:41.432 --> 10:42.391
Bye.

11:29.563 --> 11:32.149
- I'll get you something to drink first.
- I don't want any.

12:47.099 --> 12:48.100
Jun-hui.

12:49.018 --> 12:52.938
You know how I think of you
and Gyeong-seon

12:53.314 --> 12:55.232
and how much I care for both of you.

12:55.316 --> 12:56.775
You already know that, right?

12:57.943 --> 13:00.446
- I do.
- Then how could you do this?

13:01.906 --> 13:04.074
Well, sure.

13:04.950 --> 13:07.411
Everyone makes mistakes.

13:07.661 --> 13:10.998
Everyone makes mistakes
once in their lifetime, right?

13:12.875 --> 13:15.920
I don't think it was a mistake
that I decided to date Jin-a.

13:17.296 --> 13:21.258
You might think so for now.

13:21.342 --> 13:23.761
That's why you took things this far.

13:24.261 --> 13:25.429
But Jun-hui,

13:26.222 --> 13:28.682
let's not complicate things like this.

13:29.016 --> 13:31.936
Both you and Jin-a have
a whole life in front of you.

13:32.102 --> 13:33.687
You shouldn't waste your time

13:33.771 --> 13:36.065
on something petty like this,
don't you think?

13:40.152 --> 13:41.153
I know

13:42.112 --> 13:43.781
you don't like what I'm saying.

13:44.823 --> 13:46.492
I know that.

13:47.243 --> 13:50.287
But what else can I say
given the position I'm in?

13:51.038 --> 13:54.208
We're like family, you know.

13:54.291 --> 13:57.711
Don't you think this whole thing
is very inappropriate?

13:59.838 --> 14:00.881
We are...

14:01.799 --> 14:04.885
just two people who fell in love.

14:05.219 --> 14:06.637
Can't you try to understand us?

14:09.098 --> 14:12.685
Can't you try to understand
why I am being like this?

14:12.977 --> 14:14.395
Can you please do that for me?

14:14.687 --> 14:17.022
I... I'll even get down on my knees
and beg you.

14:17.106 --> 14:19.483
- Jun-hui, please. I'm begging you.
- Ms. Kim.

14:19.567 --> 14:21.235
- Please don't...
- I'm begging you.

14:21.318 --> 14:22.319
Ms. Kim.

14:24.196 --> 14:25.364
Please get up.

14:28.701 --> 14:31.620
You understood everything I said, right?

14:32.288 --> 14:33.664
Right?

14:35.875 --> 14:36.834
No.

14:54.310 --> 14:56.395
I know that I lack in many ways.

14:58.063 --> 14:59.231
Because I know that,

14:59.315 --> 15:01.150
I want to prove that I can better myself

15:01.233 --> 15:03.527
not only to Jin-a but to you and Mr. Yoon.

15:04.820 --> 15:06.530
Please trust me and give me a chance.

15:14.204 --> 15:15.372
Right.

15:16.957 --> 15:18.500
It's you of all people.

15:19.168 --> 15:21.045
I should be completely honest with you.

15:22.922 --> 15:23.881
You do know...

15:24.465 --> 15:27.551
that I have high standards
for other people, right?

15:31.263 --> 15:33.390
You don't meet my standards.

15:36.685 --> 15:39.605
I know that people call someone
like me a snob

15:40.022 --> 15:43.067
and even accuse them of using
their children to get what they want.

15:43.359 --> 15:44.401
I don't care what they say.

15:45.069 --> 15:45.945
Why?

15:46.403 --> 15:48.113
Because I'm being like that
for my children.

15:48.489 --> 15:51.200
Every parent wants the best
for their children,

15:51.283 --> 15:52.952
not anything less than that.

15:54.244 --> 15:56.246
In my opinion,

15:56.330 --> 15:58.123
no parent would ever
compromise their standards

15:58.207 --> 16:00.501
unless they have no choice to.

16:02.252 --> 16:04.213
If Jin-a's father had not retired already,

16:04.296 --> 16:06.090
I would've aimed higher.

16:07.132 --> 16:08.092
Do you think

16:08.175 --> 16:10.803
I'm being like this because I think
Jin-a owes me for raising her?

16:11.095 --> 16:12.262
Not at all.

16:13.639 --> 16:16.058
I'm doing this because I want
not only Jin-a and Seung-ho

16:16.141 --> 16:18.894
but even their children
to have a better life.

16:19.561 --> 16:21.772
You need power to live a better life.

16:22.731 --> 16:24.817
What gives you power
in a capitalist society?

16:24.900 --> 16:26.402
Where do you think success comes from?

16:30.447 --> 16:33.450
I'm still young.

16:34.034 --> 16:35.411
- In the future--
- Gosh.

16:36.120 --> 16:37.955
You're smarter than that.

16:39.456 --> 16:43.585
I know that you understand
every word I'm saying.

16:44.753 --> 16:47.589
I won't tell others
that you gave in to me.

16:48.215 --> 16:49.216
So don't be stubborn.

16:51.552 --> 16:53.012
I'm sorry,

16:53.721 --> 16:55.180
but I can't give up on Jin-a.

16:56.557 --> 16:58.475
No matter what you say, I can't.

16:59.268 --> 17:00.728
I can never give up on her.

17:02.604 --> 17:06.233
Don't make me hurt you even more.
Please don't make things harder.

17:25.461 --> 17:26.920
I don't want to say this

17:27.463 --> 17:28.964
as much as you don't want to hear it.

17:30.215 --> 17:33.302
Let's forget about everything
that has happened between us

17:33.635 --> 17:36.388
and put things back
to how they used to be.

17:36.472 --> 17:37.639
I'm sorry.

17:40.017 --> 17:41.935
I can't do as you please.

17:45.606 --> 17:47.232
Are you saying you'll go against me?

17:49.234 --> 17:52.821
If that's how you interpreted it,
I guess that's what it is.

17:55.449 --> 17:59.119
I thought too highly of you.

17:59.661 --> 18:01.163
I thought you knew better than this.

18:03.582 --> 18:04.708
I'm sorry.

18:06.752 --> 18:09.254
I can't live without Jin-a.

18:31.485 --> 18:32.820
Why did you lie?

18:33.904 --> 18:35.697
Why did you lie to me? Why?

18:37.032 --> 18:39.159
Shut it. Follow me out.

18:41.328 --> 18:43.413
Is this the best you can do?

18:44.498 --> 18:45.999
Do you call this your best?

18:46.083 --> 18:47.709
How dare you talk to me like that?

18:49.169 --> 18:50.504
What did I do wrong?

18:51.255 --> 18:52.756
Tell me. What did I do wrong?

18:52.840 --> 18:55.467
Do you think you did nothing wrong?
Is that what you think?

18:55.551 --> 18:56.593
Yes!

18:58.011 --> 18:59.304
You're unbelievable.

18:59.888 --> 19:03.100
What were you guys doing?
What were you doing here?

19:03.934 --> 19:05.269
Exactly what you're thinking of.

19:07.521 --> 19:10.023
Why? Should I just tell you straight up?

19:11.191 --> 19:14.695
You little brat. Get off her. Right now!

19:14.945 --> 19:17.364
I told you to get off her!

19:17.447 --> 19:18.657
Stop it!

19:18.740 --> 19:19.658
- Get off!
- Stop it.

19:19.741 --> 19:21.451
Get off her!

19:21.535 --> 19:23.078
Stop hitting him!

19:23.787 --> 19:26.540
- Jin-a.
- Move!

19:28.125 --> 19:29.334
Jin-a.

19:30.460 --> 19:31.753
I'm okay. I really am.

19:33.547 --> 19:36.300
Don't lie to me. You're not okay.

19:37.759 --> 19:40.470
Why do you always say that you're okay?

19:46.143 --> 19:47.269
Follow me.

20:15.005 --> 20:16.215
I'm okay.

20:23.889 --> 20:25.182
I'm okay, too.

20:27.184 --> 20:28.769
I can get through anything.

20:32.314 --> 20:33.398
I'll go now.

23:44.631 --> 23:47.968
Jin-a must have gone to work already.

23:48.885 --> 23:50.470
Did she say she had to leave early today?

23:51.304 --> 23:52.139
Did she?

23:53.723 --> 23:54.891
That day

23:55.725 --> 23:58.436
when you took Jin-a out
for some morning exercise,

23:58.562 --> 23:59.980
was she really sleeping in her room?

24:00.856 --> 24:02.315
Of course.

24:02.399 --> 24:03.859
You'd better not be lying.

24:04.734 --> 24:05.694
Of course I'm not.

24:07.696 --> 24:12.367
You should think about the consequences
of your actions.

24:12.492 --> 24:14.578
Otherwise, you will end up
regretting everything.

24:26.423 --> 24:27.966
Hey, Jin-a. It's been a while.

24:28.049 --> 24:29.759
I almost forgot your face.

24:29.968 --> 24:32.721
That's why I came to update you
on the store.

24:33.430 --> 24:35.932
Don't bother telling me anything
if things aren't any better.

24:37.350 --> 24:38.810
You're making me feel uneasy.

24:39.686 --> 24:41.396
Even if you focus on your job,

24:41.521 --> 24:43.607
you might not be able to
make things work at the store.

24:43.690 --> 24:46.318
You should've spent less time
with your boyfriend.

24:48.987 --> 24:51.740
If that's why you slacked off,
you deserve some disciplinary action.

24:53.950 --> 24:56.203
I'll accept the punishment
if I deserve it.

24:58.788 --> 24:59.956
Oh, right.

25:00.040 --> 25:02.626
Did you enjoy the movie with Mr. Gong?

25:03.335 --> 25:05.295
It was a movie about bromance.

25:05.378 --> 25:07.422
That's why I gave you two tickets.

25:07.505 --> 25:09.966
But I forgot to tell you
that I gave one to each of you.

25:10.050 --> 25:11.635
Did you guys meet at the theater?

25:12.344 --> 25:14.387
Well... It was nice.

25:15.013 --> 25:17.474
The movie... The movie was nice.

25:17.891 --> 25:18.892
That's a relief.

25:19.601 --> 25:20.852
I envy you.

25:23.438 --> 25:24.606
- Let's go.
- Yes.

25:32.447 --> 25:33.949
What is it?

25:35.992 --> 25:37.160
Yoon Jin-a is here.

25:38.787 --> 25:40.622
So what? There's nothing strange
about that.

25:41.122 --> 25:43.833
Mr. Jo called her to his office
as soon as she came in.

25:45.752 --> 25:47.420
What if she talks?

25:48.129 --> 25:50.674
You said you're innocent.

25:50.924 --> 25:52.008
Of course.

25:52.092 --> 25:54.511
All I did was try to get along
with the employees.

25:54.594 --> 25:55.679
You know that.

25:57.806 --> 25:58.807
Or don't you?

26:00.183 --> 26:01.893
My opinion isn't important.

26:01.977 --> 26:04.688
What matters is
what the female employees think.

26:06.982 --> 26:08.566
What do you think their opinion is?

26:10.277 --> 26:11.695
What you should worry about now

26:12.279 --> 26:14.281
is how you're going to survive this.

26:15.991 --> 26:17.367
How I would survive?

26:18.118 --> 26:20.829
Hey, what do I need to do?
How can I get away with this?

26:28.586 --> 26:29.629
Mr. Nam?

26:31.673 --> 26:32.674
Right.

26:33.717 --> 26:35.552
If one of the executives takes the bullet,

26:37.137 --> 26:38.596
it won't be dragged out.

26:41.599 --> 26:43.685
I know some who hold grudges against him.

26:46.938 --> 26:48.315
Thanks. Thanks a lot.

27:07.208 --> 27:10.337
Well, I guess I'll have to review it again
later on.

27:10.920 --> 27:12.922
I'm not totally satisfied with it,

27:13.631 --> 27:15.050
but you did a pretty good job.

27:15.800 --> 27:17.177
I'll try harder.

27:18.303 --> 27:19.804
You should return to the office soon.

27:20.347 --> 27:22.515
We can't keep a competent employee
like you at the store.

27:23.892 --> 27:25.810
Thank you for thinking highly of me.

27:26.686 --> 27:27.854
Do you not want to come back?

27:28.146 --> 27:30.106
You don't seem so excited about it.

27:33.151 --> 27:34.235
No, I do.

27:37.364 --> 27:39.616
The problem
that's been bothering the female employees

27:39.949 --> 27:41.284
is actually more serious

27:41.785 --> 27:43.620
than what has been reported to me, right?

27:46.122 --> 27:47.207
I was one of those

27:47.916 --> 27:51.086
who tried not
to make a big deal out of it.

27:51.878 --> 27:52.921
So I have been

27:53.546 --> 27:57.050
thinking about
what I could have done differently.

27:58.051 --> 28:01.971
Hence, I can't really say
anything about it at the moment.

28:02.847 --> 28:03.848
However,

28:05.183 --> 28:08.103
I'm going to make sure
I speak up this time.

28:10.563 --> 28:13.191
Yes, you should.
That'd be the right thing to do.

28:14.984 --> 28:16.194
Have some tea.

28:17.070 --> 28:18.071
Thank you.

28:31.418 --> 28:34.379
"The color of the lipstick
you're wearing today is very sexy."

28:35.964 --> 28:38.508
"Did you smile at me at the karaoke bar?"
And a heart emoji?

28:38.800 --> 28:41.010
Hey, you guys should've cursed at him.

28:41.094 --> 28:42.971
Why did you send him
the smiley face emoji?

28:43.138 --> 28:45.306
I had to send something to shut him up.

28:45.807 --> 28:48.685
Gosh, how disgusting.
This is making me want to barf.

28:48.768 --> 28:50.770
Goodness, what the hell is this?

28:52.564 --> 28:55.024
It happens all the time
especially during our company dinners,

28:56.234 --> 28:57.610
so I guess I got used to it.

28:58.027 --> 29:00.280
I started neglecting the issue altogether
at some point.

29:02.073 --> 29:05.076
That's why I can't remember
any specific incidents.

29:06.911 --> 29:08.246
Then there's nothing we can do.

29:10.999 --> 29:12.041
But you see,

29:13.793 --> 29:15.628
I'm a bit worried about you guys.

29:17.964 --> 29:19.090
Pardon me?

29:19.674 --> 29:21.801
They say that a rotten apple

29:21.885 --> 29:23.636
can spoil the whole barrel.

29:23.970 --> 29:27.265
I know you guys haven't done
anything wrong,

29:27.849 --> 29:29.225
but you might get dragged into it.

29:30.518 --> 29:33.855
To tell you the truth, I think that's
what Mr. Jo is worried about the most.

29:34.647 --> 29:36.566
- Mr. Jo?
- Yes.

29:38.026 --> 29:40.653
Let's just hope that doesn't happen.

29:41.738 --> 29:43.114
I mean, it should not.

29:43.698 --> 29:45.116
If any of you are falsely accused,

29:47.786 --> 29:48.953
I won't be able to stand it.

29:58.338 --> 29:59.631
Well...

30:02.050 --> 30:03.593
What is it?

30:03.676 --> 30:06.763
- I didn't intentionally record this video.
- Okay.

30:06.846 --> 30:09.265
I just recorded it for fun
during our company dinner.

30:10.183 --> 30:11.226
Okay.

30:12.060 --> 30:13.144
Show me.

30:30.078 --> 30:32.121
We're doing this for you.

30:32.288 --> 30:33.915
You can't just keep backing out of it.

30:34.916 --> 30:36.125
It's not like that.

30:36.292 --> 30:38.419
If it doesn't get resolved properly,

30:38.795 --> 30:41.047
we'll just end up humiliating ourselves.

30:41.714 --> 30:43.967
And no one can guarantee
that they will not get back at us.

30:44.634 --> 30:46.261
What if we get fired?

30:47.178 --> 30:50.014
Even if we don't get fired,
we'll end up quitting

30:50.098 --> 30:51.808
because of the way people judge us.

30:52.058 --> 30:54.686
Totally.
It'll be hard to find another job,

30:54.769 --> 30:56.688
but even if we do,
the rumor will follow us.

31:01.025 --> 31:02.819
What do you think we should do, Se-yeong?

31:04.863 --> 31:06.447
Let's hope that everything goes well.

31:07.031 --> 31:08.992
That sounded so insincere.

31:10.034 --> 31:12.704
I do feel bad for saying this,

31:13.538 --> 31:15.540
but fortunately, you and I...

31:17.041 --> 31:19.043
aren't the victims of this matter.

31:19.919 --> 31:21.880
We should be understanding
of their situations.

31:22.630 --> 31:24.841
I don't think we should force them
to come forward.

31:26.801 --> 31:29.512
It'd be a good idea
to give them some time to think.

31:31.514 --> 31:34.017
Let's meet another time
and exchange our opinions.

31:38.563 --> 31:39.898
Let's talk another time.

32:14.557 --> 32:15.683
Come in.

32:31.157 --> 32:32.116
Here you go.

32:47.048 --> 32:49.968
APPROVAL NEEDED

34:00.455 --> 34:03.207
Gosh, Jin-a...

34:48.044 --> 34:49.087
Here you go.

34:49.170 --> 34:51.464
As usual, there's nothing to point out

34:52.298 --> 34:55.384
even though I really wanted to find faults
because you hurt my feelings.

34:56.135 --> 34:57.220
What did I do?

34:58.513 --> 35:00.306
Yoon Jin-a and Seo Jun-hui.

35:02.350 --> 35:04.936
It's not like I was their matchmaker
or something.

35:05.103 --> 35:06.687
I was shocked by the news as well.

35:07.730 --> 35:09.065
What did your parents say?

35:09.982 --> 35:11.526
You said they're very picky.

35:12.360 --> 35:14.153
Do they think she's good enough for him?

35:15.655 --> 35:17.782
They'll never think anyone
is good enough for him.

35:19.283 --> 35:21.494
Does that mean they disapprove of her?

35:21.577 --> 35:23.412
You are getting too excited.

35:25.998 --> 35:27.208
Don't get me wrong.

35:27.792 --> 35:29.418
- Enjoy your drink.
- Thank you.

35:34.966 --> 35:36.300
I don't want it.

35:37.468 --> 35:40.513
I boiled these because you said
it's hard for you to eat regular food.

35:43.057 --> 35:45.059
Your friends...

35:45.226 --> 35:47.270
Some of them are still working, right?

35:48.020 --> 35:49.063
Yes.

35:49.564 --> 35:51.607
Can you ask them
if they can help Jin-a out?

35:52.024 --> 35:53.776
We can't force her to date someone else.

35:53.943 --> 35:55.611
Even parents can't do that.

35:56.028 --> 35:58.156
I'm talking about a job.

35:58.489 --> 36:00.032
Does she want to quit her job?

36:00.366 --> 36:03.035
- I'm going to make her quit.
- What are you talking about?

36:03.578 --> 36:05.538
We have to break them apart.

36:05.621 --> 36:07.957
And your solution is
making her quit her job?

36:08.666 --> 36:10.209
What is the matter with you?

36:10.293 --> 36:13.045
Besides, it's not easy
to find a job these days.

36:13.588 --> 36:16.340
That's why I'm asking you
to pull some strings.

36:16.424 --> 36:17.675
Stop talking nonsense.

36:18.092 --> 36:19.135
Gosh...

36:20.052 --> 36:22.680
You worked for over 30 years,

36:22.763 --> 36:25.474
yet you don't even have any connections.

36:27.268 --> 36:30.396
If you managed to keep your position
at work,

36:30.479 --> 36:33.274
Jun-hui would never have dared
to go out with Jin-a.

36:34.233 --> 36:35.902
How lowly does he think of us?

36:35.985 --> 36:38.613
I can't believe he thinks
he deserves to date our daughter.

36:39.697 --> 36:42.408
Fine, it's all my fault.
I'm responsible for everything.

36:42.491 --> 36:43.784
So what do you want me to do?

36:43.868 --> 36:46.120
Should I write up a resume
and look for a job?

36:46.829 --> 36:48.539
Get a job if you can.

36:48.623 --> 36:51.876
I can't believe you just said that!
How could you say such a thing to me?

36:56.088 --> 36:57.673
Why does he get so worked up?

37:25.534 --> 37:26.661
My gosh.

37:46.180 --> 37:49.308
Did we go through too many of them?
I just can't decide on one.

37:50.226 --> 37:52.311
Did the Chinese company
ask for anything specific?

37:52.478 --> 37:54.647
I don't think they have
anything specific in mind.

37:54.730 --> 37:56.399
We'll have to come up with something.

37:57.066 --> 37:58.859
When will we start joining them?

37:59.151 --> 38:00.486
As soon as they set everything up.

38:01.487 --> 38:03.739
We still have some time.

38:08.077 --> 38:10.162
Are you still unwilling to go?

38:11.706 --> 38:12.707
Yes.

38:13.249 --> 38:15.418
Don't you have any loyalty
for the company--

38:15.501 --> 38:17.253
I stayed in the States for three years.

38:19.755 --> 38:22.258
I have some things to wrap up,
so I will excuse myself.

38:25.344 --> 38:28.306
He became so brazen
ever since he started dating.

38:30.641 --> 38:33.561
- Right?
- Yes, it's so annoying.

38:38.774 --> 38:40.234
My gosh.

38:46.615 --> 38:47.700
Hey, Jun-hui.

38:49.910 --> 38:51.829
You need to stop crossing the line.

38:53.331 --> 38:55.416
What if you end up getting fired?

38:55.833 --> 38:56.959
Then I'll get fired.

38:57.501 --> 38:58.502
Hey.

38:59.545 --> 39:01.547
I know you are in love,
but get a grip, all right?

39:03.341 --> 39:05.134
It's not that easy.

39:12.266 --> 39:13.726
Do you have time?

39:15.561 --> 39:16.604
Why?

39:18.439 --> 39:19.482
Let's eat.

39:30.242 --> 39:32.745
- You startled me.
- My gosh.

39:34.580 --> 39:37.500
Gosh, they're both weird.

40:05.277 --> 40:08.280
I'm not asking anything because you'll say
everything went fine with your mom.

40:09.573 --> 40:12.743
To be exact, nothing happened at all.

40:13.285 --> 40:14.412
That's a relief.

40:17.581 --> 40:19.375
She must have been very understanding.

40:24.755 --> 40:26.882
You don't need to force yourself
to say that.

40:28.676 --> 40:30.302
You can get angry all you want.

40:30.719 --> 40:32.388
You can totally bad-mouth my mom.

40:32.638 --> 40:34.265
I'm totally fine with that.

40:34.974 --> 40:37.685
"Why is she so dismissive of me
when her daughter isn't any better?"

40:37.768 --> 40:40.771
You can bad-mouth her like that
and get angry. I won't mind it at all.

40:41.355 --> 40:43.357
I can take everything you say
without getting upset.

40:45.484 --> 40:46.819
I'm disappointed in you.

40:50.823 --> 40:53.325
I know very well
what kind of person you are.

40:53.742 --> 40:56.412
But you're purposely saying
all those bad things because of me.

40:56.704 --> 40:59.623
And you look so determined
to do worse at home.

41:00.833 --> 41:03.752
Don't be like that.
You're only making me feel uneasy.

41:08.424 --> 41:09.967
It's because I'm upset.

41:10.384 --> 41:13.053
Think about how I would feel
when you say or do things you don't mean.

41:14.930 --> 41:17.933
I told you that I'm fine with everything.

41:18.851 --> 41:22.229
I'm fine as long as you don't get hurt.

41:24.023 --> 41:26.442
Are you telling me to sit back
and watch you suffer?

41:27.067 --> 41:29.904
Why would you put it that way?
You'll stay by my side at all times.

41:40.039 --> 41:41.123
Like this?

41:42.958 --> 41:45.085
Yes, like this.

41:45.544 --> 41:47.087
Are you still disappointed in me?

41:48.172 --> 41:49.715
No. I like you so much that it kills me.

41:50.090 --> 41:52.510
You can't die without my permission.

41:53.385 --> 41:54.720
Then what can I do?

41:57.932 --> 41:58.974
Nothing.

42:01.602 --> 42:02.853
Don't move your hand.

42:03.771 --> 42:07.024
See? I can even control your body now.

42:07.816 --> 42:09.443
- My gosh.
- Raise your right leg.

42:09.568 --> 42:10.694
Raise your left arm.

42:11.487 --> 42:14.823
- Look at that.
- I really can't beat you.

42:14.949 --> 42:16.200
Did you think you could beat me?

42:16.617 --> 42:18.160
Well, not exactly.

42:24.750 --> 42:25.876
What?

42:26.877 --> 42:30.589
Are you worried that someone
who shouldn't know about us might pass by?

42:33.801 --> 42:35.135
You're crazy.

42:38.138 --> 42:39.890
Why? What's wrong?

42:40.182 --> 42:42.518
Is there a guy
who shouldn't know about us passing by?

42:44.895 --> 42:46.146
Wait. Wait.

42:46.772 --> 42:48.691
Why? Come here.

42:48.774 --> 42:50.442
Okay, fine.

42:50.526 --> 42:52.152
What are you fine with?

43:49.501 --> 43:50.544
Thank you.

44:30.250 --> 44:31.251
Where are you going?

44:31.794 --> 44:33.754
I'm going to meet Gyeong-seon.

44:36.173 --> 44:37.966
You can come with me
if you can't believe me.

44:40.135 --> 44:42.054
Take your medicine. I won't be late.

45:09.748 --> 45:11.792
You can suspect me
if anything goes missing.

45:12.167 --> 45:15.587
You should take everything
while you're at it. You're so dumb.

45:18.799 --> 45:21.093
Then are you dating Jin-a
because you're so smart?

45:22.636 --> 45:24.138
Why are you dating her?

45:28.892 --> 45:29.977
Because she's pretty.

45:33.939 --> 45:34.982
Gosh, that idiot.

45:40.571 --> 45:41.905
Why haven't you called me?

45:42.614 --> 45:44.700
It feels like you're upset with me
or something.

45:46.452 --> 45:48.454
You know I don't like
walking on eggshells.

45:49.830 --> 45:51.206
It's because I know

45:51.582 --> 45:54.168
your mom will nag you
for hanging out with me.

45:55.586 --> 45:57.546
She won't nag me.

45:59.339 --> 46:02.134
So are you saying
you're going to keep this up?

46:03.302 --> 46:05.721
I don't want you to get scolded
because of me.

46:05.804 --> 46:07.139
I'd rather stay quiet.

46:11.226 --> 46:13.437
You and Jun-hui
must've been born just for me.

46:16.565 --> 46:19.651
I must've been a soldier in my past life,
and saved both you and Jun-hui's lives.

46:19.818 --> 46:22.779
I think you guys are here
to repay me in this life.

46:23.280 --> 46:24.948
Do you want me to beat you up?

46:26.992 --> 46:28.368
I'm being sincere.

46:30.537 --> 46:32.247
Who else would care for me this much?

46:33.582 --> 46:35.459
You always put up
with all the stress alone.

46:38.754 --> 46:40.672
Is Jun-hui having a hard time?

46:45.844 --> 46:47.012
You know he doesn't show it.

46:57.314 --> 46:59.191
Should we have just one drink, my friend?

47:01.026 --> 47:02.903
Should we do that, my friend?

47:03.946 --> 47:05.572
- Bring it here.
- Okay.

47:07.407 --> 47:08.408
Just one drink?

47:10.285 --> 47:11.870
Hey, let's make a bet.

47:12.412 --> 47:13.789
Seung-ho wants to make a bet.

47:15.457 --> 47:18.835
Jin-a, don't cause trouble and go home.

47:20.170 --> 47:21.088
You heard that, right?

47:23.215 --> 47:26.134
Okay, don't drink too much.

47:28.387 --> 47:29.429
Just one drink.

47:31.306 --> 47:33.642
Okay, I'll call you later.

47:39.982 --> 47:41.149
Gosh.

47:42.609 --> 47:43.527
Sorry.

47:43.610 --> 47:46.405
Gosh, I shouldn't have come.
You are so annoying.

47:48.240 --> 47:51.034
This is why everyone
should listen to their mothers.

47:53.453 --> 47:54.955
She told me not to hang out with you.

47:57.708 --> 47:59.585
It's unlike you to defy her.
You're a mama's boy.

48:02.087 --> 48:03.130
Hey.

48:03.755 --> 48:06.675
Let me give you a tip.

48:08.176 --> 48:11.930
Every mother in this world
loves playing a role.

48:12.306 --> 48:14.808
That's why I decided to
become a mama's boy.

48:15.350 --> 48:16.935
If I act like an immature kid,

48:17.436 --> 48:19.938
she'll think that she still needs
to care for me.

48:20.188 --> 48:23.233
She might nag me,
but she'll feel good on the inside.

48:26.069 --> 48:27.821
So what's your tip?

48:29.239 --> 48:32.284
Well, this actually applies to Jin-a.

48:32.909 --> 48:35.662
She should act like she needs Mom's help.

48:36.038 --> 48:38.707
Then she should try to win Mom over
by acting all immature.

48:40.125 --> 48:41.668
But she's immature anyway.

48:43.378 --> 48:44.880
I'm sure it'll work.

48:47.424 --> 48:50.135
You know your mom very well,

48:50.385 --> 48:51.678
but you know nothing about Jin-a.

48:52.888 --> 48:53.764
In what way?

48:54.389 --> 48:55.223
In every way.

48:57.601 --> 48:58.727
Whatever.

48:59.728 --> 49:00.979
You think Jin-a changed?

49:01.897 --> 49:03.774
Sure, she did.

49:04.524 --> 49:06.443
She's only like this today
because of Gyeong-seon.

49:06.902 --> 49:08.236
That's just how Jin-a is.

49:08.820 --> 49:09.738
You're wrong.

49:10.364 --> 49:11.823
How much do you know about her?

49:13.033 --> 49:15.285
- What about you?
- I'm her brother.

49:16.620 --> 49:17.788
I'm her boyfriend.

49:22.459 --> 49:25.087
Did you decide to be all brazen now?

49:25.295 --> 49:27.547
Hey, try calling me your brother-in-law.

49:28.632 --> 49:30.050
- Brother-in-law, my foot.
- Hey.

49:30.133 --> 49:32.469
- Brother-in-law?
- Stop it.

49:32.636 --> 49:35.430
- You deserve a beating.
- I'm sorry.

49:35.514 --> 49:36.765
- I'm sorry.
- Do you want to die?

50:00.956 --> 50:03.083
The fact that

50:03.166 --> 50:05.460
We have a clueless tomorrow

50:05.627 --> 50:08.088
Is a very exciting thing

50:08.171 --> 50:10.966
Although it may be scary

50:11.508 --> 50:15.220
That's what life is

50:15.429 --> 50:18.557
No one can know the future

50:19.015 --> 50:21.393
Hey, wait. Isn't that my brother?

50:21.643 --> 50:22.978
It's Jun-hui.

50:23.395 --> 50:24.438
- Jun-hui.
- Hey.

50:26.106 --> 50:28.150
Hey, he's my brother.

50:28.233 --> 50:29.568
He's my boyfriend.

50:30.360 --> 50:32.696
Hey, I'm your sister-in-law.

50:33.905 --> 50:35.532
My goodness, my sister-in-law.

50:37.284 --> 50:38.326
Gosh.

50:48.128 --> 50:49.838
- Why did you drink so much?
- Cheers.

50:51.256 --> 50:52.174
Cheers.

51:01.057 --> 51:02.267
That's a turnoff, right?

51:02.809 --> 51:03.852
She's cute.

51:05.187 --> 51:06.271
Hey, get lost.

51:06.938 --> 51:07.939
Get out of my sight.

51:14.613 --> 51:15.530
Sure.

51:17.574 --> 51:18.492
Go on.

51:41.765 --> 51:42.808
Seung-ho.

51:44.142 --> 51:47.813
I never asked you
for any kind of favors until now.

51:49.648 --> 51:50.941
Why are you getting so serious?

51:51.900 --> 51:54.736
Okay, I'll be there for Jun-hui
when he needs me.

51:54.861 --> 51:56.571
No, it's about Jin-a.

51:56.947 --> 51:58.490
Please be there for her.

51:58.740 --> 52:00.450
That's what you can do for Jun-hui.

52:03.036 --> 52:05.664
I know what you mean.

52:07.082 --> 52:09.209
You probably already thought about this,

52:09.668 --> 52:11.253
but no one knows...

52:13.547 --> 52:15.006
what might happen to them.

52:16.049 --> 52:17.092
But personally,

52:17.509 --> 52:20.637
I'm going to make sure
that I don't lose my friend

52:21.179 --> 52:22.305
no matter what.

52:24.516 --> 52:27.310
That's what I'm going to do,
so I want you to do the same.

52:28.979 --> 52:30.438
Shouldn't you be asking me

52:30.939 --> 52:33.024
instead of giving me orders?

52:33.733 --> 52:35.777
Just do what I tell you to do.

52:35.944 --> 52:37.571
I don't like Jun-hui that much.

52:37.904 --> 52:39.906
Even so, stick by his side.

52:39.990 --> 52:41.783
Don't make any other best friends.

52:42.659 --> 52:44.119
You can't force that upon me.

52:44.202 --> 52:46.288
I have my own thoughts and preferences.

52:50.250 --> 52:51.793
Do you hate Jun-hui that much?

52:52.961 --> 52:54.087
My gosh.

52:54.170 --> 52:57.424
Will you do me a favor
if I get on my knees and plead?

52:58.341 --> 53:00.343
Seung-ho, please be there for him.

53:00.886 --> 53:01.928
I'm being sincere.

53:02.262 --> 53:03.430
What are you doing? Stop it.

53:03.513 --> 53:05.515
- You little jerk.
- What are you doing?

53:05.599 --> 53:08.101
If I tell you to do something, just do it.

53:08.184 --> 53:10.270
How dare you talk back to me like that?

53:10.770 --> 53:12.480
- Okay. Stop it.
- Just do as I say.

53:14.482 --> 53:15.817
My gosh.

53:16.943 --> 53:18.653
Let's not betray each other.

53:21.281 --> 53:22.115
Cheers.

54:54.791 --> 54:57.544
I'm not going to force you to testify.

54:58.712 --> 55:01.297
And I won't blame you
even if you choose not to.

55:01.715 --> 55:02.716
Just know

55:04.676 --> 55:07.095
that I feel uneasy for burdening you

55:07.262 --> 55:08.763
with something like this.

56:13.620 --> 56:17.207
I'm Yoon Jin-a, an assistant manager
of the franchise operations team.

56:18.249 --> 56:21.795
I'd like to share
what I experienced in the last ten years

56:22.420 --> 56:25.799
working as a supervisor.

56:32.472 --> 56:36.184
Everything is based on facts,

56:36.392 --> 56:39.395
and I'm willing to give testimony
whenever it's necessary.

56:53.618 --> 56:55.495
Oh, hello.

56:55.620 --> 56:59.124
Hey, you must be doing all the housework
because of your mom's injury.

56:59.207 --> 57:01.167
Well, not everything.

57:01.501 --> 57:03.169
You will make a good wife.

57:04.546 --> 57:06.589
- Get home safely.
- Thank you. Take care.

57:06.673 --> 57:07.757
Bye.

57:21.688 --> 57:23.690
Why are three people needed
just to set the table?

57:23.773 --> 57:25.150
Just sit down, Seung-ho.

57:25.733 --> 57:28.319
- After I do this.
- Sit down already. It's so distracting.

57:38.371 --> 57:39.539
- Eat up.
- Okay.

57:42.417 --> 57:43.751
It's 3 p.m. today.

57:45.628 --> 57:48.882
I told you to make yourself available
for a blind date this weekend.

57:50.884 --> 57:53.178
It's already been arranged,
so you have to be there.

57:53.761 --> 57:55.472
- Mom.
- Be quiet.

57:55.680 --> 57:58.349
I'm going to find a nice guy for her,
end of discussion.

57:59.601 --> 58:02.228
Do you think
we're like those rich families or what?

58:02.729 --> 58:05.231
Don't you think blind dates
are so old-fashioned?

58:06.232 --> 58:09.319
That's what rich families do
for their children.

58:09.652 --> 58:11.237
Shut your mouth, will you?

58:11.821 --> 58:12.822
I told you it's at 3 p.m.

58:14.741 --> 58:15.825
I have plans today.

58:16.826 --> 58:17.911
What?

58:18.661 --> 58:21.372
Didn't you hear me?
I said I have plans today.

58:21.706 --> 58:22.832
Don't even start with me.

58:26.794 --> 58:27.795
Mom.

58:29.923 --> 58:30.882
Just do as I say, okay?

58:32.217 --> 58:34.636
Don't.
You don't need to listen to your mom.

58:34.719 --> 58:37.222
No, I'll scold you if you do as she says.

58:38.389 --> 58:39.807
What do you think you are doing now?

58:39.891 --> 58:42.685
Look who's talking. You didn't even
ask her if she'd be up for it.

58:43.520 --> 58:45.605
I know she's our child,
but you can't order her around.

58:46.272 --> 58:47.857
What is wrong with you? Show some class!

58:48.566 --> 58:49.734
What did you just say?

58:49.943 --> 58:51.694
How dare you!
How could you say such a thing?

58:52.278 --> 58:53.321
I can say whatever I want!

58:54.614 --> 58:55.740
Dad.

58:56.574 --> 58:57.867
And you too.

58:58.117 --> 59:00.411
Why can't you speak up
when you don't want to do something?

59:02.664 --> 59:05.667
I'm going to say something as the head
of this family. From now on,

59:06.042 --> 59:08.503
we'll put everyone's freedom first.
If you go against it,

59:08.586 --> 59:09.796
I'll kick you out of my house!

59:30.984 --> 59:32.819
You went too far this time.

59:39.909 --> 59:43.621
Gosh, why should I care
whether you want to cook for her or not?

59:43.705 --> 59:45.498
Is Jin-a my girlfriend?

59:45.957 --> 59:47.333
No, she's all mine.

59:48.668 --> 59:51.629
- You little...
- I don't know what ingredients to buy.

59:51.796 --> 59:52.797
Let's go together.

59:53.006 --> 59:56.050
I can't even bad-mouth her
because she's my friend.

59:56.259 --> 59:58.344
What's there to bad-mouth about?
She's so adorable.

59:58.428 --> 01:00:01.222
- You little...
- Gosh, again? Wait, someone's calling you.

01:00:10.732 --> 01:00:11.691
You can answer it.

01:00:12.650 --> 01:00:15.486
It's an important call.
You should go home now.

01:00:16.070 --> 01:00:17.071
Go on.

01:00:53.983 --> 01:00:54.859
Hey.

01:00:55.902 --> 01:00:56.819
Where are you going?

01:00:57.820 --> 01:00:59.489
I have to run an errand for my mom.

01:01:00.114 --> 01:01:01.449
Shall I come with you?

01:01:01.783 --> 01:01:03.034
No, it's okay.

01:01:03.993 --> 01:01:05.119
When will you be back?

01:01:05.787 --> 01:01:07.372
It won't take too long.

01:01:07.705 --> 01:01:09.624
Let's have dinner together
instead of lunch.

01:01:10.833 --> 01:01:12.877
Well, that's fine, but...

01:01:15.088 --> 01:01:17.965
All right, then. Call me when you're done.

01:01:19.050 --> 01:01:20.051
Sorry.

01:01:20.802 --> 01:01:21.886
Why?

01:01:22.178 --> 01:01:23.888
Because I broke my promise.

01:01:25.723 --> 01:01:28.017
Not really.
We're just pushing it back by a few hours.

01:01:28.601 --> 01:01:29.686
Either way.

01:01:32.730 --> 01:01:34.232
Are you sure you can go by yourself?

01:01:34.774 --> 01:01:37.568
I'm very self-sufficient.

01:01:38.569 --> 01:01:40.446
Gosh, I'm so proud of you.

01:01:40.947 --> 01:01:43.950
I'll call you later.
Don't cry even if you miss me a lot.

01:01:47.412 --> 01:01:50.581
- Stop it.
- Okay. Call me.

01:02:10.184 --> 01:02:12.019
I can't go grocery shopping with you.

01:02:12.186 --> 01:02:13.688
Something came up at the store.

01:02:51.100 --> 01:02:53.478
Jin-a, you're such a good daughter.

01:02:54.604 --> 01:02:57.648
You even do what you don't want to do
because you don't want to upset your mom.

01:02:58.065 --> 01:02:59.734
You really are all grown up now.

01:03:02.236 --> 01:03:05.114
Yes, just meet the guy briefly

01:03:05.198 --> 01:03:07.158
so that your mom won't be upset.

01:03:07.241 --> 01:03:10.453
It's better than clashing with her.
In the long run, it'll help you

01:03:11.078 --> 01:03:12.747
persuade her...

01:03:13.206 --> 01:03:14.373
Dad.

01:03:15.249 --> 01:03:18.294
I know that you're trying to help me,

01:03:19.086 --> 01:03:21.464
but doing things like that
will only worsen my situation.

01:03:22.089 --> 01:03:23.633
I really meant it.

01:03:24.217 --> 01:03:25.635
I know.

01:03:26.719 --> 01:03:28.262
I know that.

01:03:28.721 --> 01:03:30.723
But Dad, I just wish for one thing.

01:03:31.140 --> 01:03:32.892
I don't want any attention.

01:03:33.267 --> 01:03:37.063
Whether at home or work,
I don't want anyone's attention.

01:03:37.271 --> 01:03:40.483
I don't want to be the center
of attention. That's my only wish.

01:03:43.778 --> 01:03:47.281
I'm going to meet the guy today,
but it's not because of Mom.

01:03:47.907 --> 01:03:49.826
I'm not doing it for you either.

01:03:50.284 --> 01:03:51.828
I'm doing it for Jun-hui.

01:03:52.620 --> 01:03:54.747
I'm going there because of Jun-hui.

01:04:07.093 --> 01:04:08.553
I'll get going.

01:04:24.819 --> 01:04:26.654
I have to go to the store briefly.

01:04:26.737 --> 01:04:27.822
Well...

01:04:29.699 --> 01:04:31.200
But why are you dressed like that?

01:04:31.993 --> 01:04:34.203
What's wrong with this?
I wear this all the time.

01:04:38.624 --> 01:04:40.668
I have something to do.
I'll tell you about it later.

01:04:40.751 --> 01:04:43.004
Tell me now, or I'll follow you.

01:04:45.673 --> 01:04:46.966
Dad's here.

01:04:49.760 --> 01:04:50.803
And?

01:04:51.554 --> 01:04:52.513
He wants to see me.

01:04:54.307 --> 01:04:55.683
So what?

01:04:55.850 --> 01:04:58.769
What? I should meet him
and hear what he has to say.

01:04:58.853 --> 01:05:01.439
Who cares what he has to say?
What difference does that make?

01:05:01.522 --> 01:05:03.316
I'll let it all out
and fight him if I want to.

01:05:03.399 --> 01:05:05.359
He's been horrible to us,
and I can't let it slide.

01:05:05.443 --> 01:05:07.612
We do have to talk to him
face-to-face at some point.

01:05:08.195 --> 01:05:09.739
I'll see you later.

01:06:27.400 --> 01:06:28.401
Jin-a.

01:06:29.652 --> 01:06:30.736
What are you doing here?

01:06:31.278 --> 01:06:32.238
Gyeong-seon.

01:06:34.407 --> 01:06:35.408
Are you here because...

01:06:37.034 --> 01:06:38.786
I can't believe this.

01:06:39.996 --> 01:06:40.997
Gyeong-seon.

01:06:42.915 --> 01:06:45.876
Can you not tell Jun-hui about this?

01:06:46.836 --> 01:06:48.295
He kind of knows already.

01:06:48.921 --> 01:06:50.006
How does he know?

01:06:50.256 --> 01:06:52.341
Did Seung-ho tell him
that I'm going on a blind date?

01:06:53.217 --> 01:06:54.260
What?

01:06:55.052 --> 01:06:57.013
That's why you're here?
Not because of my dad?

01:06:57.888 --> 01:07:00.016
Are you actually here for a blind date?

01:07:01.517 --> 01:07:03.394
Jin-a, are you crazy?

01:07:03.769 --> 01:07:05.146
Have you lost your mind?

01:07:05.438 --> 01:07:07.857
What about Jun-hui?
Have you been toying with him?

01:07:09.358 --> 01:07:11.360
Gyeong-seon, let me explain. It's--

01:07:11.902 --> 01:07:13.195
End it with Jun-hui.

01:07:13.738 --> 01:07:15.197
Unbelievable.

01:07:45.644 --> 01:07:47.605
- Aren't you Jin-a?
- The fact that she was there

01:07:47.688 --> 01:07:49.690
means that they have no respect for you.

01:07:49.774 --> 01:07:52.151
They're treating you
as if you don't exist.

01:07:52.234 --> 01:07:55.029
- Is Jun-hui going abroad again?
- I guess Ms. Yoon didn't know about it.

01:07:55.112 --> 01:07:57.490
He never gives anyone a second chance.

01:07:57.573 --> 01:08:00.868
I'm not sure if Yoon Jin-a
would be okay if this gets out.

01:08:00.951 --> 01:08:02.787
- Gosh.
- Are you okay, Mr. Nam?

01:08:02.870 --> 01:08:04.997
Can I meet Jun-hui?

01:08:05.081 --> 01:08:07.500
What else could I possibly do for you?

01:08:09.919 --> 01:08:10.878
Why didn't you call me?

01:08:11.587 --> 01:08:12.755
I was scared.

01:08:13.964 --> 01:08:14.882
That I might get angry?

01:08:16.133 --> 01:08:17.885
That you might ignore my call.

01:08:17.968 --> 01:08:19.136
I'm going to do as I please.

01:08:20.930 --> 01:08:21.847
Do what?

01:08:23.224 --> 01:08:24.892
I'm going to love you and care for you.

01:08:25.935 --> 01:08:26.977
I can't even do that?

01:08:27.478 --> 01:08:29.480
Subtitle translation by Lee Ja-won
